snippet.title: Invisibox Trailer (Puzzle Game for PC and Mobile)
snippet.description:
Invisibox is a minimalistic puzzle game for PC and Mobile Devices that is now available on Itch.io, Steam, Play Store and App Store.
Get the game: 

http://retrific.net/invisibox-game.php

Invisibox is a tricky puzzle game where you have to solve sliding puzzles by controlling invisible boxes while avoiding various obstacles.

Get Invisibox right now on invisibox.retrific.net
